  "content": {
    "type": "procedural",
    "format": "markdown",
    "body": "### Collaboration Workflow\n1. **AI Proposal**: AI generates suggested nodes during chat or ingestion, which enter the review_queue.\n2. **Human Review**: Users periodically check the queue to refine, merge, or reject proposals.\n3. **Commit**: Approved knowledge becomes part of the permanent Evergreen graph."
